OL,6,FCelebrity auctioneer and TV antiques
OL,7,Fexpert, Charles Hanson, has been
OL,8,Funanimously cleared of coercive
OL,9,Fbehaviour allegations made against him
OL,10,Fby his wife Rebecca.
OL,12,FJurors deliberated for around four-and-
OL,13,Fa-half hours before acquitting the
OL,14,FBargain Hunt and Antiques Road Trip
OL,15,Fexpert of two assault charges relating
OL,16,Fto incidents in 2015 and 2023, and a
OL,17,Fseparate charge of controlling and
OL,18,Fcoercive behaviour spanning from 2015
OL,19,Fto 2023.
