OL,3,CBargain Hunt auctioneer Charles Hanson
OL,4,Ccleared of coercive control and assault
OL,6,FThe television personality has also
OL,7,Fappeared on Flog It! and Antiques Road
OL,8,FTrip and runs auction houses in
OL,9,FDerbyshire and Staffordshire.
OL,11,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,12,Fdomestic incident at the star's home
OL,13,Fin the village of Quarndon,
OL,14,FDerbyshire, in June last year.
OL,16,FA three week trial at Derby Crown
OL,17,FCourt heard how Hanson was accused of
OL,18,Fusing violence towards Mrs Hanson over
OL,19,Fa 10-year period, including pushing,
OL,20,Fscratching and grabbing her.
