OL,4,Ccleared of coercive control and assault
OL,6,FFollowing the verdict, Hanson smiled
OL,7,Fat his parents and gave a thumbs-up
OL,8,Fgesture from the dock after the jury
OL,9,Fforeman returned the not guilty
OL,10,Fverdicts.
OL,12,FThe celebrity auctioneer's parents,
OL,13,Fwho were sitting in the front row of
OL,14,Fthe public gallery, wept and hugged
OL,15,Ftheir son after he was discharged from
OL,16,Fthe dock.
OL,18,FJudge Martin Hurst thanked the jurors
OL,19,Ffor their care in considering the case.
