OL,6,FHe then told Hanson: "You have been
OL,7,Ffound not guilty. That is the end of
OL,8,Fthe case. You will hear no more about
OL,9,Fit and you are free to go."
OL,11,FMr Hanson told the trial at Derby
OL,12,FCrown Court that he was "almost a
OL,13,Fslave" to his wife, who left him "a
OL,14,Fbeaten and broken man" by controlling
OL,15,Fhim and making him subservient to her.
