OL,3,CBargain Hunt auctioneer Charles Hanson
OL,4,Ccleared of coercive control and assault
OL,6,FShe claimed he was violent towards
OL,7,Fher, putting her in a headlock in 2012
OL,8,Fwhile she was pregnant with a baby she
OL,9,Flater lost, repeatedly "grabbed" her,
OL,10,Fpushed her twice during a bedroom row,
OL,11,Fand scratched her as she tried to
OL,12,Fsnatch a mobile phone.
OL,14,FBut the jury of seven women and five
OL,15,Fmen cleared Mr Hanson after being
OL,16,Finvited to consider whether he was
OL,17,F"lying to get out of trouble" or if
OL,18,Fhis wife had given an exaggerated
OL,19,Faccount to the court.
