OL,6,FMr Hanson, of Ashbourne Road,
OL,7,FMackworth, Derby, told jurors his wife
OL,8,Fwas allowed "to do what she wanted"
OL,9,Fbut had experienced "moments and
OL,10,Fepisodes" including an incident in
OL,11,Fwhich she claimed his legs being
OL,12,Fcrossed amounted to abuse.
OL,14,FHanson's defence in their closing
OL,15,Fspeech invited the jury to find the 46-
OL,16,Fyear-old not guilty.
