OL,6,FSasha Wass KC told the jury Rebecca
OL,7,F"used this court as an extension of
OL,8,Fher divorce battle" and has "dismally
OL,9,Ffailed to satisfy the standards
OL,10,Frequired" to prove her case.
OL,12,FSpeaking to reporters immediately
OL,13,Foutside the courtroom, Charles Hanson
OL,14,Fsaid: "I'm delighted that after a year
OL,15,Fand a half the truth has finally come
OL,16,Fout. I can finally live my life again.
OL,17,FI feel this burden has finally been
OL,18,Flifted."
